### Machine Learning API Endpoints

### Get ML Feature Vectors (All Data)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ml/features
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Get ML Feature Vectors (Sampled and Shuffled)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ml/features?format=vector&include_metadata=true&sample_size=100&shuffle=true
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Get ML Feature Vectors (Without Metadata)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ml/features?format=vector&include_metadata=false&sample_size=50&shuffle=false
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Get ML Training Data (Default Split)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ml/training-data
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Get ML Training Data (Custom Split)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ml/training-data?test_size=0.3&random_state=123
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Get ML Training Data (Small Test Split)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ml/training-data?test_size=0.1&random_state=42
Accept: {{contentType}}

